# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# SAFETY WHITELIST
# This git repo (remote: mclaugjo2003/DealSight) is rooted at the home folder
# C:\Users\mclau. To stop personal files (passwords, API keys, SSH keys, other
# projects) from ever being committed, ignore EVERYTHING by default and allow
# only the DealSight project plus the repo-root files Streamlit Cloud deploys.
# Note: this does not untrack files already committed — only blocks new ones.
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# 1) Ignore everything at the repo root
/*

# 2) Re-allow the repo-root files Streamlit Cloud deploys from
!/.gitignore
!/requirements.txt
!/runtime.txt

# 3) Re-allow ONLY the DealSight project (must walk each parent of the path)
!/Documents
/Documents/*
!/Documents/Python Projects
/Documents/Python Projects/*
!/Documents/Python Projects/Dealsight_rental_analyzer

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Global ignores (also apply inside the allowed project)
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Python
__pycache__/
*.py[oc]
build/
dist/
wheels/
*.egg-info

# Environments / deps
.venv
node_modules

# Next.js
.next/
out/

# Secrets & local env (never commit these)
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
**/.streamlit/secrets.toml
